sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant U as Student
  participant FE as Frontend
  participant APP as app.go
  participant ING as ingestion.Service
  participant DB as SQLite
  participant TE as taskengine.Service
  participant SY as sync.Service

  U->>FE: Select file
  FE->>APP: IngestDocument(filePath, notebookName)
  APP->>ING: RegisterDocument()
  ING->>DB: Insert documents(status=pending)
  APP->>ING: ProcessRegisteredDocument(documentID)
  ING->>DB: Update status=processing
  ING->>ING: Extract text and chunk by heading
  ING->>DB: Insert chunks and mark document ready

  Note over TE: Planned wiring in next sprint
  APP-->>TE: BuildLearningPath(notebookID, documentID)
  TE->>DB: Upsert topics + create daily_tasks

  FE->>APP: CompleteReviewSession(...)
  APP->>SY: Enqueue(flashcard_session event)
  SY->>DB: Insert sync_queue(status=pending)

  FE->>APP: RunManualSync()
  APP->>SY: RunManualSync(limit)
  SY->>DB: Local status transitions only
  Note over SY: HTTP POST /sync is planned next